    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-06-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-06-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="34"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d34">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Wharton</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-06-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 23, 1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Egan, in view of the strong desire expressed to him by the minister for
                    foreign affairs for a prompt and friendly settlement of the claims growing out
                    of the <hi rend="italic">Baltimore</hi> incident to be made with the minister of
                    the United States, asks that particulars be sent to him at the earliest date
                    practicable.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
